{"tid":597731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假鈔「紅衫魚」殺入香港，OK便利店伏已中！","createTime":"2018-03-19T02:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T03:25:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc75aed9ea88600f0b2c92f78c462c5970fd4216","tid":597731,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180318/large/1521367398_dba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180318%2Flarge%2F1521367398_dba6.jpg&h=0533bd34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一段提醒市民留意偽鈔的短片在網上流傳，拍片人表示收到三張100港元偽鈔，又指是在東涌收到。警方證實，昨日收到一名姓顧女子報案，指前日在東涌站OK便利店為八達通增值100元，給與店員500元後獲找贖回4張100元，但當中三張100港元懷疑為偽鈔，案件現交由大嶼北分區警署跟進。記者下午到過相關的便利店，店員承認昨晚有警員到場調查，但對事件不知情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180318/57963060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57963060&d=e%2FsC%2FBdbtYRdGnAOuN7emS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3abc6653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57963060&h=1e78ff56\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180318/57963060</a>"},{"pid":"3e1559eacc67a81c4ae9e46c948a8e52dd723d98","tid":597731,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"根據該段影片顯示，三張100港元懷疑偽鈔的編號分別為SZ151402、SZ151402及SZ151443，其中兩張編號相同，片中有男聲形容懷疑偽鈔「好膠吓摸落去，各位小心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180318/large/1521353807_66cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180318%2Flarge%2F1521353807_66cd.jpg&h=7c92b856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOK便利店發言人晚上回覆《蘋果》指非常關注事件，會全力配合及協助警方調查。發言人又表示，一向有內部標準收驗鈔票程序，亦有定時安排培訓給前線服務專員。公司亦再次提醒前線同事加強對大額鈔票的核實。"},{"pid":"5ae940a9ebf0da3b5ce80cfa5f62a2430c983db7","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"毒果又為支那寶入侵制造社會輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb1ae0807a42c4b22e4c9f6fbf4ee428200fb09","tid":597731,"uid":2613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5ae940a9ebf0da3b5ce80cfa5f62a2430c983db7","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"毒果又為支那寶入侵制造社會輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"咁老老實實<br />\n唔通唔報咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5066ae2a5fb8299b9718847b3ab7f0848f28437","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"beb1ae0807a42c4b22e4c9f6fbf4ee428200fb09","tid":597731,"uid":2613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5ae940a9ebf0da3b5ce80cfa5f62a2430c983db7","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"毒果又為支那寶入侵制造社會輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"咁老老實實<br />\n唔通唔報咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"網上流傳短片....<br />\n毒果記者點解又同黑警跟既"},{"pid":"c3f1f318fba138133452b11ba45a88461cf30e7a","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"beb1ae0807a42c4b22e4c9f6fbf4ee428200fb09","tid":597731,"uid":2613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5ae940a9ebf0da3b5ce80cfa5f62a2430c983db7","tid":597731,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"毒果又為支那寶入侵制造社會輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:21:34.000Z","m